reaches new heights.

300
00:26:13,040 --> 00:26:14,910
Reach new heights!

301
00:26:19,430 --> 00:26:20,520
Hello, everyone.

302
00:26:20,630 --> 00:26:22,320
We're having an amazing guest today.

303
00:26:22,800 --> 00:26:23,720
She's currently

304
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,080
the most popular food blogger

305
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:29,240
