of "Kaixi's Kitchen",

306
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:30,800
Ms. Chen Kaixi.

307
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:32,109
Let's give her a round of applause.

308
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:32,670
Welcome.

309
00:26:33,040 --> 00:26:34,560
Hello everyone, I'm Chen Kaixi.

310
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,430
Hello.

311
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:36,150
