Aussie...

315
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:45,280
Let's welcome Ms. Chen Kaixi.

316
00:26:47,350 --> 00:26:48,560
I read

317
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:49,960
your script.

318
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:52,150
Ms. Xi, you're busy,

319
00:26:52,150 --> 00:26:53,590
yet you found time

320
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,190
to read my script.

321
00:26:56,390 --> 00:26:58,870
