324
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:02,760
It's inspired by life.

325
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,080
It comes from life.

326
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:04,800
Besides,

327
00:27:05,150 --> 00:27:06,150
the setting

328
00:27:06,190 --> 00:27:07,800
