332
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,150
A crazy dummy.

333
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:15,480
Ms. Kaixi, you haven't
finished reading yet.

334
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:17,760
There's a plot twist later.
It's amazing.

335
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:18,910
I wish I could act in it.

336
00:27:18,910 --> 00:27:20,670
When's the pitch?

337
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,830
Pitch?

338
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:23,960
It should be

339
00:27:24,022 --> 00:27:25,422
before the Chinese New Year.

340
00:27:25,670 --> 00:27:26,670
I'll go with you.

341
00:27:26,870 --> 00:27:27,590
Really?

342
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:28,240
Are you sure?

343
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:28,590
Yes.

344
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:30,140
Do I get the honor of having you there?

345
00:27:30,390 --> 00:27:32,320
If you come, a lot of people
will want to invest.

346
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:33,390
Then I want to go to.

347
00:27:33,630 --> 00:27:36,240
Aren't you afraid people will find out
you're the inspiration?

348
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:38,040
Didn't you say
nobody would find out it's me?

349
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:38,670
I did,

350
00:27:38,870 --> 00:27:40,630
but I can add on my slides:

351
00:27:40,870 --> 00:27:43,080
"Ms. Chen Kaixi, thank you

352
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:46,630
for your huge contributions
to this script."

353
00:27:46,630 --> 00:27:49,240
I'm fine with that.
That's free publicity.

354
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:51,150
Can you put

355
00:27:51,150 --> 00:27:52,480
my brand logo there too?

356
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,760
Oh gosh, Xi...

357
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:57,080
You're really a businessperson now.

358
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,480
So practical.

359
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:01,040
I like it.

360
00:28:06,910 --> 00:28:08,430
Cheers.

361
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:12,240
Happy Chinese New Year!
Let's all get rich!

362
00:28:13,155 --> 00:28:15,240
Qingcheng, how many endorsements
do you have now?

363
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:17,150
I can see you everywhere these days.

364
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:20,560
My team is putting in some effort,

365
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:21,911
so there are quite a few.

366
00:28:22,320 --> 00:28:22,870
That's great.

367
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:23,960
See?

368
00:28:24,320 --> 00:28:26,280
You're popular

369
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:28,000
and capable

370
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,560
so brands are chasing you now.

371
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:30,430
That's right.

372
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,560
Capability matters.

373
00:28:33,350 --> 00:28:34,520
By the way, Qingcheng,

374
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:37,480
I really have to thank you.

375
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:39,960
If you hadn't taken me onto the
variety show,

376
00:28:40,066 --> 00:28:41,830
I wouldn't have gained popularity
so fast.

377
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:44,240
There's no need

378
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,910
to bring this up.

379
00:28:45,910 --> 00:28:47,040
No, I have to.

380
00:28:48,644 --> 00:28:49,910
Speaking of variety shows,

381
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,000
Xi,

382
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:53,430
can you consider

383
00:28:53,630 --> 00:28:55,630
Di Di's dating show?

384
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:57,240
It's all upside.

385
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:58,190
If you join,

386
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,870
first, you can promote

387
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:00,960
your band.

388
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:02,190
Second,

389
00:29:02,870 --> 00:29:03,480
I want to

390
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:06,520
see you dating some cute
and handsome guy

391
00:29:06,800 --> 00:29:09,080
and flirting with them

392
00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:11,110
on TV

393
00:29:11,870 --> 00:29:13,080
to teach them something.

394
00:29:13,190 --> 00:29:13,800
That'd be fun.

395
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:17,590
Forget it.

396
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:18,960
Tiao is still young.

397
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:21,350
Maybe when he's older.

398
00:29:23,150 --> 00:29:23,960
Is Tiao

399
00:29:24,630 --> 00:29:25,630
back in Shanghai?

400
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:29,430
His dad picked him up.

401
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,080
His grandparents came.

402
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,644
It's the end of the year now.

403
00:29:32,670 --> 00:29:34,111
It's good to let him be with them.

404
00:29:40,150 --> 00:29:41,350
Chen Mian

405
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:43,430
wants to buy back the shares.

406
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,240
So

407
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:52,670
what do you think?

408
00:29:55,150 --> 00:29:56,190
Well,

409
00:29:56,910 --> 00:29:58,280
let's see who's more patient.

410
00:30:06,190 --> 00:30:07,320
Please enjoy the food.

411
00:30:09,560 --> 00:30:10,280
Zhou.

412
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:19,870
This really hits the spot.

413
00:30:19,933 --> 00:30:22,755
Way better than the cold buffet
at our company's year-end dinner.

414
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,320
At least it's hot.

415
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,350
But speaking of which,

416
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:31,960
a divorced guy like me slipped away
from the dinner is understandable.

417
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,240
You are

418
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:34,870
a promising bachelor.

419
00:30:34,870 --> 00:30:36,150
Why did you run?

420
00:30:36,760 --> 00:30:38,080
There are many pretty ladies

421
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:39,480
at the office.

422
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,670
None of them caught your eye?

423
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:42,520
Or

424
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,040
is someone

425
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:47,390
still on your mind,

426
00:30:47,630 --> 00:30:48,760
and you don't want to settle?

427
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:50,280
Enough about me.

428
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:53,080
You think I don't know why you run away?

429
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:55,350
It's because that woman

430
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:56,480
saw through you.

431
00:30:57,320 --> 00:30:59,280
You're the president
of a listed company.

432
00:30:59,622 --> 00:31:00,760
Attractive and promising.

433
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:02,800
But, in fact, you're just
a high-level employee.

434
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:06,720
What you earn goes to your ex-wife.

435
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,190
Zhou, I've known you for years

436
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:12,910
and never realized

437
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:14,910
you had such a mouth on you.

438
00:31:15,390 --> 00:31:16,760
Did you learn that from Luo Man?

439
00:31:16,910 --> 00:31:18,350
Luckily, you two broke up.

440
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,110
Back in the day,

441
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:29,040
I chased girls,

442
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:32,320
but now girls chase me.

443
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,390
I get nervous about that.

444
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:36,960
Do you know why?

445
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:37,800
Why are you nervous?

446
00:31:39,670 --> 00:31:40,830
Women know exactly

447
00:31:40,830 --> 00:31:42,110
what kind of man

448
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:43,080
they marry.

449
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,280
But men?

450
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:46,080
You sleep next to her

451
00:31:47,830 --> 00:31:50,830
for over a decade

452
00:31:52,430 --> 00:31:54,350
and still don't truly know her.

453
00:31:56,150 --> 00:31:56,830
Am I

454
00:31:58,150 --> 00:31:59,720
really stupid?

455
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:03,350
Yes.

456
00:32:06,150 --> 00:32:06,910
Me too.

457
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:08,960
But there's one thing I do better.

458
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:11,350
I...

459
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:13,590
I never underestimated

460
00:32:13,590 --> 00:32:14,910
any woman.

461
00:32:32,110 --> 00:32:33,870
Chen Kaixi.

462
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:40,150
I missed her,

463
00:32:42,430 --> 00:32:44,080
and I feel bad.

464
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:50,960
What's wrong?

465
00:32:52,390 --> 00:32:53,870
The garlic smell is stinging my eyes.

466
00:32:58,280 --> 00:33:00,480
What's with that look? It's the garlic.

467
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:03,520
Zhou,

468
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:05,800
why do I feel like
we're both so unlucky?

469
00:33:07,666 --> 00:33:09,266
You can drop the "feel like" part.

470
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:13,040
Come on, drink.

471
00:33:15,430 --> 00:33:18,500
(Beijing-Styled Copper Hotpot)

472
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:21,720
Isn't this Fang Chi?

473
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:25,080
He's got so many fans now.

474
00:33:25,390 --> 00:33:26,720
Just one random post on Weibo

475
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,320
gets thousands of comments.

476
00:33:28,430 --> 00:33:29,320
Really?

477
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:31,430
A lot of people are shipping him
with another girl.

478
00:33:31,688 --> 00:33:32,870
This female doctor, right?

479
00:33:32,870 --> 00:33:34,190
It's her, right?

480
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,190
Man,

481
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:42,040
what's going on
between you and Fang Chi?

482
00:33:47,390 --> 00:33:48,720
It's like

483
00:33:50,910 --> 00:33:52,630
when you're tired,

484
00:33:53,590 --> 00:33:54,910
you wish to see him.

485
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,040
After seeing him,

486
00:33:57,630 --> 00:34:00,240
you can hold on a little longer.

487
00:34:01,190 --> 00:34:02,670
It's hard to explain.

488
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,960
You're starting to sound like

489
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:10,110
Zhou Musun now.

490
00:34:10,790 --> 00:34:12,750
Can you not pick up his bad habit?

491
00:34:12,750 --> 00:34:13,590
Right.

492
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,560
Say something useful.

493
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,270
Have you two

494
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:18,750
done it?

495
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,520
Right, have you...

496
00:34:20,533 --> 00:34:21,520
You know what I mean.

497
00:34:22,670 --> 00:34:23,750
Hey.

498
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:25,790
Are you seriously asking that
so directly?

499
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:27,110
How indirectly should we ask then?

500
00:34:27,110 --> 00:34:27,630
How?

501
00:34:27,750 --> 00:34:28,310
Wait.

502
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:31,460
Can't we talk about something
more spiritual?

503
00:34:31,460 --> 00:34:32,960
- I'm not interested.
- Not interested.

504
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:33,710
Spill it. Come on.

505
00:34:33,710 --> 00:34:34,790
Yeah. Quick.

506
00:34:34,790 --> 00:34:35,750
Stop asking.

507
00:34:36,310 --> 00:34:37,520
My head's a mess right now.

508
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:40,040
Good.

509
00:34:40,040 --> 00:34:42,110
A messy head is good.

510
00:34:42,170 --> 00:34:43,933
You're so invested
that you're confused.

511
00:34:43,955 --> 00:34:45,270
I see hope here.

512
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:47,480
I give up.

513
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,360
Happy Chinese New Year.

514
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:53,920
You too.

515
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:55,100
Let us know when you get home.

516
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,040
Rest up early.

517
00:34:56,040 --> 00:34:56,520
Sure.

518
00:34:56,520 --> 00:34:57,040
Bye.

519
00:34:58,790 --> 00:34:59,880
Big star forever!

520
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:01,080
You can do this!

521
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:02,670
Bye.

522
00:35:06,155 --> 00:35:08,230
She has to work even
on the first day of the year.

523
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:10,270
That's tough.

524
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,520
You're not leaving today, are you?

525
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:15,400
No.

526
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,520
I'm staying with you tonight.

527
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:34,230
What are you still thinking about?

528
00:35:36,270 --> 00:35:37,400
I just think

529
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:39,480
Fang Chi is pretty good.

530
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:41,670
Sure,

531
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,590
he can't compare to Zhou Musun.

532
00:35:43,790 --> 00:35:44,480
But

533
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,960
if you're still thinking in those terms,

534
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:49,040
you won't be so torn.

535
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:51,150
I never

536
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:52,360
compare them.

537
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:53,310
They are

538
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,150
different.

539
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,520
The problem is

540
00:36:00,790 --> 00:36:02,310
he's so young.

541
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:04,480
His life is full of unknowns.

542
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,590
If I get together with him,

543
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:08,960
our relationship is
also full of unknowns.

544
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:10,750
I'm busy with my work.

545
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:11,790
I don't have

546
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:13,150
the energy

547
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:15,520
for that kind of relationship.

548
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:16,710
So...

549
00:36:17,790 --> 00:36:19,080
What's wrong with being young?

550
00:36:21,270 --> 00:36:23,000
Isn't that a good thing?

551
00:36:25,310 --> 00:36:26,360
Besides,

552
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:28,480
Fang Chi may be young,

553
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:30,150
but he's reliable.

554
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,000
Right?

555
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,190
What are you afraid of?

556
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,270
I'm afraid of

557
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:38,670
getting hurt.

558
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:47,000
I know Fang Chi is a reliable man.

559
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:50,040
But can you be sure

560
00:36:50,750 --> 00:36:52,080
that he won't change?

561
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:54,960
Will he turn out
to be another Zhou Musun

562
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:56,710
or Chen Mian?

563
00:36:57,270 --> 00:36:57,840
Right?

564
00:36:59,310 --> 00:37:00,670
You're right, though.

565
00:37:01,750 --> 00:37:03,080
I'm scared.

566
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:04,880
I surrender.

567
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:09,590
After the last relationship,

568
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:12,190
I've lost faith

569
00:37:12,840 --> 00:37:15,040
in people

570
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:17,400
and in love.

571
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,750
To be blunt,

572
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,520
I can't love anymore.

573
00:37:26,670 --> 00:37:29,040
You're describing me and Chen Mian.

574
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:32,630
Oh, come on.

575
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,750
Don't get sensitive.

576
00:37:34,750 --> 00:37:35,400
Gosh.

577
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,960
I'm not being sensitive.

578
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:40,710
It's just...

579
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,080
Man,

580
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:44,880
you know what?

581
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:46,750
In life,

582
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,790
the only constant

583
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:51,560
is change.

584
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,310
People

585
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:56,110
change.

586
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:57,960
You will.

587
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,080
He will.

588
00:37:59,080 --> 00:38:00,360
Everyone will.

589
00:38:00,790 --> 00:38:02,360
Look at me.

590
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:05,630
Change

591
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:08,000
