701
00:47:33,960 --> 00:47:35,270
But I believe

702
00:47:36,360 --> 00:47:38,880
beyond that,

703
00:47:39,590 --> 00:47:42,560
all women are allies.

704
00:47:43,590 --> 00:47:45,400
The relationships between women

705
00:47:45,400 --> 00:47:46,560
can be

706
00:47:47,440 --> 00:47:48,270
complex,

707
00:47:49,440 --> 00:47:50,360
ever-changing,

708
00:47:50,960 --> 00:47:51,880
and profound.

709
00:47:52,920 --> 00:47:55,230
They can be enemy

710
00:47:55,790 --> 00:47:57,110
or friends,

711
00:47:58,230 --> 00:48:01,880
or even dear enemies.

712
00:48:03,670 --> 00:48:05,150
My story

713
00:48:05,520 --> 00:48:07,630
depicts a group of such women who,

714
00:48:08,310 --> 00:48:11,040
after understanding each other's lives,

715
00:48:11,710 --> 00:48:12,750
extend a hand

716
00:48:13,000 --> 00:48:14,400
to one another

717
00:48:14,670 --> 00:48:16,150
and to themselves.

718
00:48:17,480 --> 00:48:18,190
Of course,

719
00:48:18,244 --> 00:48:20,230
there's a little personal
sentiment in this too.

720
00:48:21,080 --> 00:48:22,960
I want to dedicate this story

721
00:48:23,590 --> 00:48:26,150
to all the lovely women

722
00:48:26,150 --> 00:48:28,040
who've graced my life.

